{"id": 1620, "genre": 1000, "title": "你经历过哪些毁了整个游戏体验的事？", "description": "玩得太激烈拽掉电源线。没保存。", "record_count": 17727, "comment_count": 92, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170412150947ajDvByq1biVSW4Ek.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-11T17:00:39Z", "questions": [{"id": 2141, "title": "你经历过哪些毁了整个游戏体验的事？", "content": "你经历过哪些毁了整个游戏体验的事？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 190616, "content": "卡在一关过不去，难度调最低也过不去，太挫败了！", "image": "img/option/option/20170411161451sI8DmNG4oiqdPeBH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 190618, "content": "被突然冲出来的恐怖游戏角色吓哭", "image": "img/option/option/20170411161635negTK1DQ5CUkI7iG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 190619, "content": "刚开始玩就查视频，直接视频通关了", "image": "img/option/option/20170411162023pLmPR8n6ZDNOSJ9Y.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 190622, "content": "查了攻略完美主义发作，有一点失误都要重新来，痛苦", "image": "img/option/option/20170411162205zEQ0W8kyiMxDsv2c.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 190623, "content": "开了作弊码，无敌过后，荣华尽享，失去乐趣", "image": "img/option/option/20170411163207Y2qkfy1PWTaVhuDE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 190627, "content": "剧情狗血，游戏走向跑偏，怒弃坑", "image": "img/option/option/20170411163218Ol7agCzkLWXxRNBS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 190628, "content": "付费玩家和免费玩家的资源过度不平衡", "image": "img/option/option/20170411163343jHCvwkmUQpYu46iN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 190629, "content": "买新游戏的速度太快，每个的游戏进度都停留在 2%", "image": "img/option/option/20170411163404e6HJP3ALn9IxKb4p.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 190631, "content": "游戏社区氛围不好，玩家之间老吵架", "image": "img/option/option/20170411163627uLD6BjkGwe2pPrZS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 190632, "content": "一整天匹配出来的队友都很糟糕", "image": "img/option/option/20170411163842MaqXy45HzAelTQ6u.gif", "praise_count